WEBVTT

00:01.160 --> 00:02.821
PREVIOUSLY ON "SALEM"...

00:02.870 --> 00:04.167
George: FORNICATOR!

00:04.200 --> 00:05.167
Isaac: [ SCREAMS ]

00:05.200 --> 00:06.929
Mr. Hale: HE SEARCHES.

00:08.770 --> 00:11.238
Captain: SO WHERE IS THE WITCH?

00:11.270 --> 00:12.476
Increase: RIGHT HERE.

00:12.510 --> 00:13.704
Captain: AAAH!

00:13.740 --> 00:15.332
Mr. Hale:
IF HE CANNOT BE STOPPED,

00:15.380 --> 00:19.510
WELL, THEN IT'S AN ENTIRELY
NEW GAME, ISN'T IT?

00:19.550 --> 00:24.340
Mrs. Hale: EVERYTHING YOUR
FATHER DOES, HE DOES FOR YOU.

00:25.050 --> 00:26.654
Anne: [ GASPS ]

00:26.690 --> 00:29.329
Cotton: I NO LONGER WANT
TO BE YOUR CUSTOMER.

00:29.360 --> 00:32.227
TRUE LOVE CANNOT BE
BOUGHT OR SOLD.

00:32.260 --> 00:33.750
John: LET'S JUST LIVE.

00:33.800 --> 00:35.893
Rose: YOU STILL LOVE JOHN ALDEN.

00:35.930 --> 00:40.367
THE GRAND RITE FERMENTS BEST
IN A LOVELESS HEART.

00:40.400 --> 00:42.664
Mary: HE SERVES AT MY BEHEST.

00:42.710 --> 00:45.702
HE WON'T COME OUT FOR YOU.

00:47.640 --> 00:49.346
Cotton: FATHER.

00:49.380 --> 00:50.904
Mary: MY DEAR INCREASE.

00:50.950 --> 00:53.771
HOW LONG MAY WE ENJOY
YOUR PRESENCE IN TOWN?

00:53.820 --> 00:57.017
Increase: UNTIL EVERY LAST
DEVIL'S WHORE OF A WITCH

00:57.050 --> 01:00.588
IN SALEM IS DEAD.

01:02.430 --> 01:03.749
[ DOG BARKING ]

01:03.790 --> 01:05.223
DEPRAVITY.

01:05.260 --> 01:06.852
CAN THERE BE A MORE APT WORD

01:06.900 --> 01:09.596
TO DESCRIBE THE CURRENT STATE
OF YOUR FAIR CITY?

01:09.630 --> 01:10.927
DRINK, PERVERSITY,

01:10.970 --> 01:13.564
ABOMINATIONS
OF EACH AND EVERY VARIETY

01:13.600 --> 01:15.033
OFFERED AND RECEIVED.

01:15.070 --> 01:17.903
AND EVEN AS WE CATER
TO OUR INNER DEMONS,

01:17.940 --> 01:20.807
WE HAVE ALLOWED ACTUAL DEMONS
TO FLOURISH!

01:20.840 --> 01:22.569
WITCH ES!

01:22.610 --> 01:24.202
Mr. Hale:
HE WAS NOT SUPPOSED TO BE HERE.

01:24.250 --> 01:25.603
Increase: LIVING VESSELS
OF GODLESSNESS.

01:25.650 --> 01:26.719
Mr. Hale: SO WHY IS HE?

01:26.750 --> 01:28.240
Increase:
THE SERPENT FROM EDEN...

01:28.280 --> 01:29.986
Mary: HE CAME TO SEE WHAT
HIS SON HAD ACCOMPLISHED.

01:30.020 --> 01:31.248
Increase:
YOU HAVE LISTENED AND...

01:31.290 --> 01:33.485
Mr. Hale:
AND WHY IS HE STAYING?

01:33.520 --> 01:36.648
Mary: HE SAW WHAT HIS SON
HAD ACCOMPLISHED.

01:36.690 --> 01:39.124
Increase: THERE ARE WITCHES
HIDDEN AMONGST US,

01:39.160 --> 01:41.128
AND YOU PEOPLE OF SALEM,

01:41.160 --> 01:45.324
SEDUCED BY DRINK AND BY FLESH,

01:45.370 --> 01:47.292
ARE HAPPILY BLINDED TO IT.

01:47.340 --> 01:48.659
STANDING BEFORE YOU,

01:48.700 --> 01:51.168
WITH THE CERTAINTY
OF THE RISING SUN,

01:51.210 --> 01:55.408
I ASSURE YOU THIS WILL CHANGE.

01:55.440 --> 01:57.943
MRS. SIBLEY.

01:57.980 --> 02:02.417
Mary: REVEREND, YOUR WORDS
ARE INSPIRATION.

02:02.450 --> 02:04.088
ENGLAND'S LOSS IS OUR GAIN.

02:04.120 --> 02:07.009
Increase: I TRUST YOUR HUSBAND'S
CONDITION IS IMPROVING.

02:07.060 --> 02:08.152
Mary: SADLY, NO.

02:08.190 --> 02:10.329
Increase:
WELL, PLEASE TELL GEORGE

02:10.360 --> 02:12.453
I SHALL VISIT HIM AGAIN
AT ONCE.

02:12.500 --> 02:15.822
PERHAPS MY PRESENCE MAY BE
OF SOME COMFORT TO HIM.

02:15.860 --> 02:17.669
Mary: OH, HOW COULD IT NOT?

02:17.700 --> 02:18.928
Both: [ MOANING ]

02:18.970 --> 02:21.234
Cotton: [ BREATHING HEAVILY]

02:28.710 --> 02:31.008
Gloriana: [ CHUCKLES ]

02:32.250 --> 02:33.717
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

02:33.750 --> 02:35.047
Cotton: I HAVE NO WORDS.

02:35.080 --> 02:36.513
Gloriana: [ CHUCKLES ]

02:36.550 --> 02:38.848
Cotton: LIKE A MAN WHO'S SEEN
THE FACE OF GOD.

02:38.890 --> 02:40.448
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

02:40.490 --> 02:43.721
ONLY AN AWED SILENCE
IS THE APPROPRIATE RESPONSE.

02:43.760 --> 02:44.727
Gloriana: [ LAUGHING ]

02:50.270 --> 02:52.329
YOUR FATHER.

02:52.370 --> 02:54.691
Cotton: AND LIKE THAT,
THE MOOD IS RUINED.

02:54.740 --> 02:56.139
Gloriana:
NO, YOUR -- YOUR FATHER.

02:56.170 --> 02:57.865
HE'S -- HE'S IN THE COMMON.

02:57.910 --> 03:01.038
Cotton: WITH A CROWD, NO DOUBT,
HANGING ON HIS EVERY WORD.

03:01.080 --> 03:04.072
Gloriana: WITH A CROWD, YES,
BUT HE'S NOT SPEAKING.

03:04.110 --> 03:06.817
Cotton: WELL, THEN YOU MUST HAVE
HIM CONFUSED WITH SOMEONE ELSE.

03:06.850 --> 03:07.748
Gloriana: [ GIGGLES ]

03:07.780 --> 03:10.146
HE'S WALKING THIS WAY.

03:10.190 --> 03:11.714
Cotton: AND BY "THIS WAY,"
YOU MEAN...

03:13.460 --> 03:15.416
Woman: [ GASPS ]

03:15.460 --> 03:19.089
Cotton:
HE CANNOT FIND ME HERE.

03:25.130 --> 03:27.690
Increase: AND WHERE BETTER TO
BEGIN OUR CLEANSING OF SALEM

03:27.740 --> 03:28.764
THAN IN ITS MOST VILE DEN?

03:28.800 --> 03:30.506
Cotton: THE BACK STAIRS.

03:30.540 --> 03:32.269
Gloriana: NO, NO, NO, NO,
Y-YOU'LL CROSS THE LANDING.

03:32.310 --> 03:33.504
Cotton: GLORIANA, MY FATHER
DOES NOT UNDERSTAND ME.

03:33.540 --> 03:35.178
HE NEVER HAS.

03:35.210 --> 03:36.848
-IF HE DISCOVERS ME --
-G|oriana: UNDER THE BED NOW.

03:36.880 --> 03:39.610
-Cotton: WHAT?!
-G|oriana: UNDER THE BED NOW!

03:49.460 --> 03:50.859
Cotton: WHERE'S MY BIBLE?

03:50.890 --> 03:52.926
Gloriana: I-I-I DON'T SEE IT!

03:58.070 --> 04:00.698
OH.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

04:00.740 --> 04:02.560
REVEREND MATH ER.

04:03.670 --> 04:05.433
Increase: YOU KNOW ME?

04:05.470 --> 04:07.631
Gloriana: IS THERE ANYONE
IN THE PROVINCE WHO DOESN'T?

04:15.180 --> 04:16.818
Increase: YOU ARE ALONE?

04:18.350 --> 04:20.818
Gloriana: NO.

04:20.860 --> 04:24.387
I'M HERE WITH MY LORD.

04:24.430 --> 04:27.422
HIS WORDS, ANYWAY.
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:27.460 --> 04:31.999
THEY OFFER GREAT COMFORT
IN THESE PERILOUS TIMES...

04:32.030 --> 04:33.964
EVEN FOR A WOMAN LIKE ME.

04:48.880 --> 04:50.745
Increase: DO YOU NOT SENSE IT?

04:50.790 --> 04:55.580
THE COMMINGLING OF SIN
AND SORCERY?

04:55.620 --> 04:58.418
TAKE A BREATH.

04:58.460 --> 04:59.950
[ BREATH ES DEEPLY ]

05:00.000 --> 05:02.696
YOU CAN ALMOST TASTE IT --

05:02.730 --> 05:04.869
SATAN'S TOXIC NECT AR,

05:04.900 --> 05:10.031
DESIGNED TO DIVERT AND DISARM.

05:20.320 --> 05:22.379
AH.

05:24.320 --> 05:28.017
THE PROPRIETRESS
OF THIS CHARMING ESTABLISHMENT.

05:28.060 --> 05:30.551
Mab: WHAT'LL IT BE TODAY,
REVEREND?

05:30.590 --> 05:32.285
THIN AND PLIANT,

05:32.330 --> 05:34.890
OR THICK AND PLAYFUL?

05:41.340 --> 05:43.558
Increase:
MIND YOUR BE'I'I'ERS, MADAM.

05:43.610 --> 05:48.229
Mab: I RUN AN HONEST HOUSE.
YOU'LL FIND NOTHING HERE.

05:48.280 --> 05:50.248
Increase: I HAVE MADE MY NAME
FINDING THINGS

05:50.280 --> 05:53.875
WHERE THERE IS NOTHING
TO BE FOUND.

06:06.530 --> 06:08.919
ORRIS ROOT?

06:08.960 --> 06:12.498
Mab: STRANGERS TRAMP IN AND OUT
OF HERE EVERY DAY.

06:12.540 --> 06:16.533
I DO NOT KNOW WHAT SUBSTANCES
THEY CARRY.

06:36.260 --> 06:38.455
Increase: HMM.

06:54.080 --> 06:56.230
CASTING STONES.

06:58.080 --> 07:01.140
SELECTMEN OF SALEM...

07:01.180 --> 07:04.513
WE'VE UNCOVERED A WITCH.

07:05.590 --> 07:07.251
[ "CUPID CARRIES A GUN" PLAYS ]

07:13.200 --> 07:15.953
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

07:16.000 --> 07:17.558
* WITCH DRUMS

07:17.600 --> 07:20.194
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

07:21.470 --> 07:24.007
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

07:24.040 --> 07:25.462
* THE WITCH DRUMS

07:25.510 --> 07:28.070
* BETTER PRAY FOR HELL

07:28.110 --> 07:33.446
* NOT HALLELUJAH

07:53.300 --> 07:55.097
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]
Mr. Hale: ONE OF OURS.

07:55.140 --> 07:57.529
EXACTLY WHAT WE FEARED THE
MINUTE HE STEPPED OFF THAT SHIP.

07:57.570 --> 07:59.936
NOW, WELL,
YOU KNOW WHAT THIS MEANS.

07:59.980 --> 08:02.005
Mary: JUST BECAUSE I DON'T SHARE
YOUR PANIC

08:02.040 --> 08:03.302
DOESN'T MEAN
I DON'T GRASP THE STAKES.

08:03.350 --> 08:05.306
Mr. Hale:
HE WILL PRESS HER FOR NAMES,

08:05.350 --> 08:07.272
AND WHOSE WILL BE SHE TEMPTED
TO PROVIDE?

08:07.320 --> 08:08.719
Tituba: SHE WAS CARELESS,

08:08.750 --> 08:10.615
LEAVING OBJECTS OF HER CRAFI'
SO CLOSE AT HAND.

08:10.650 --> 08:13.289
Mr. Hale: AND FOR THAT
CARELESSNESS, WE MAY ALL BURN,

08:13.320 --> 08:14.958
TO SAY NOTHING OF WHAT
WILL BECOME OF OUR GRAND RITE.

08:14.990 --> 08:17.879
Mary: YOUR HYSTERIA
OFFERS NO SOLUTIONS.

08:17.930 --> 08:20.819
MAB SIMPLY NEEDS TO BE REMINDED
WHAT IS EXPECTED OF HER.

08:20.860 --> 08:22.669
Tituba: HER SILENCE.

08:22.700 --> 08:24.167
Mr. Hale: [ SIGHS]
YOU'RE RIGHT.

08:24.200 --> 08:25.895
I SHALL PAY HER A VISIT AT ONCE.

08:30.340 --> 08:31.830
Tituba: YOU'RE WORRIED.
[ DOOR OPENS ]

08:31.870 --> 08:34.532
Mary: HE IS FORMIDABLE,
THE SENIOR MATHER,

08:34.580 --> 08:38.004
PART BULLY, PART BLOODHOUND.

08:38.050 --> 08:41.542
Tituba: MAB HAS BEEN LOYAL
TO THE HIVE THROUGHOUT.

08:41.580 --> 08:44.048
Mary: IT IS NOT MAB
THAT WORRIES ME.

08:44.090 --> 08:47.059
INCREASE PROMISES TO PAY
ANOTHER VISIT.

08:47.090 --> 08:49.012
HOW LONG BEFORE HE REALIZES

08:49.060 --> 08:51.153
THAT GEORGE IS NOT SICK,
BUT SPELLED?

08:51.190 --> 08:53.397
AND AT WHOSE HANDS? MINE.

08:53.430 --> 08:55.250
Tituba: THEN PREVENT THIS.

08:55.300 --> 08:57.427
Mary: YES.

08:58.870 --> 09:01.088
INCREASE MAY VISIT
AT HIS PLEASURE,

09:01.140 --> 09:04.598
FOR WHAT LOVING WIFE WOULD LEAVE
HER AILING HUSBAND AT HOME

09:04.640 --> 09:07.438
WHEN HIS CONDITION DEMANDS
ATTENTION AT ONCE?

09:13.150 --> 09:15.072
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

09:23.290 --> 09:24.689
John:
YOU'RE DRINKING EARLY TODAY.

09:24.730 --> 09:26.254
Cotton:
IF YOU KNEW MY FATHER,

09:26.290 --> 09:28.394
YOU'D COMMEND ME
FOR WAITING THIS LONG.

09:28.430 --> 09:30.591
John:
YOU KNOW, THE WAY YOU SPEAK
OF HIM, YOU MAKE HIM SOUND --

09:30.630 --> 09:31.961
Cotton: INHUMAN?

09:32.000 --> 09:34.093
-John: YES.
-Cotton: GOOD.

09:34.140 --> 09:37.359
THEN I HAVE PAINTED
AN ACCURATE PICTURE.
[ DOOR OPENS ]

09:37.410 --> 09:41.039
DON'T BELIEVE ME?
SEE FOR YOURSELF.

09:41.080 --> 09:42.536
[ SIGHS ]

09:42.580 --> 09:43.877
Increase: COTTON,

09:43.910 --> 09:46.071
I'VE BEEN IN SEARCH OF YOU
ALL MORNING.

09:46.110 --> 09:48.044
I SUPPOSED
I SHOULD HAVE REALIZED

09:48.080 --> 09:51.015
YOU WOULD BE SOMEWHERE
WHERE WHISKEY IS SERVED.

09:52.090 --> 09:53.057
Cotton: FATHER, THIS IS JOHN --

09:53.090 --> 09:54.557
Increase: JOHN ALDEN.

09:54.590 --> 09:58.321
YOUR FATHER AND I WERE
CLASSMATES AT UNIVERSITY.

09:58.360 --> 09:59.793
John: YES, I KNOW.

09:59.830 --> 10:01.957
Increase: AN HONOR, CAPTAIN.

10:02.000 --> 10:04.560
TRULY, I CAN HAVE
NO GREATER RESPECT

10:04.600 --> 10:07.489
THAN FOR A MAN WHO HAS RISKED
HIS LIFE IN BA'I'I'LE.

10:07.540 --> 10:12.671
SADLY, NOT ALL YOUNG MEN POSSESS
THE SAME ME'I'I'LE.

10:12.710 --> 10:15.178
Cotton:
WHAT BRINGS YOU, FATHER?

10:15.210 --> 10:17.508
Increase:
WELL, I AM SHOCKED TO DISCOVER

10:17.550 --> 10:21.008
THE EXTENT OF THE DEPRAVITY
AND IMMORALITY IN SALEM.

10:21.050 --> 10:25.089
THE PEOPLE NEED A REMINDER
OF THE WAGES OF THEIR SIN.

10:25.120 --> 10:26.678
Cotton:
AND SO THEY WILL GET ONE.

10:26.720 --> 10:28.915
-Increase: MM-HMM.
-Cotton: IN SUNDAY'S SERMON.

10:28.960 --> 10:30.780
Increase: NO. NO.

10:33.360 --> 10:36.625
THEY NEED TO HEAR
YOUR VOICE NOW.

10:36.670 --> 10:39.264
A PUBLIC RECITATION
ON THE COMMONS,

10:39.300 --> 10:41.837
ILLUSTRATED BY THE FACE OF SIN.

10:41.870 --> 10:44.759
Cotton: THE FACE OF SIN?

10:44.810 --> 10:47.631
AND WHO IS THAT?

10:49.380 --> 10:52.440
Increase: AND, COTTON?

10:52.480 --> 10:54.539
YOUR BIBLE.

11:23.880 --> 11:25.302
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

11:25.350 --> 11:28.342
Mary: THE HOSPITAL IN BOSTON
AWAITS HIM.

11:28.380 --> 11:30.348
IT IS MY ONLY HOPE
TO FIND A CURE

11:30.390 --> 11:32.085
FOR HIS WORSENING CONDITION.

11:32.120 --> 11:34.054
[ HORSE SNORTS ]

11:35.790 --> 11:38.224
[ HORSE WHINNIES ]

11:38.260 --> 11:42.549
AND, ISAAC, YOUR FEELINGS
TOWARDS MY HUSBAND

11:42.600 --> 11:44.568
FOR WHAT HE ONCE DID --

11:44.600 --> 11:46.090
TH EY'RE UNDERSTAN DABLE,

11:46.130 --> 11:48.439
BUT TO HELP HIM
IN HIS HOUR OF NEED

11:48.470 --> 11:50.768
SHOWS ME
THE TRUE MEASURE OF YOU...

11:50.810 --> 11:53.938
FOR WHICH I AM
FOREVER GRATEFUL.

11:53.980 --> 11:56.904
[ HORSE WHINNIES ]

11:56.950 --> 11:59.407
Isaac: WE WILL BE IN BOSTON
BY DAYBREAK.

11:59.450 --> 12:00.678
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

12:00.720 --> 12:02.369
[ HOOVES CLOPPING ]

12:25.310 --> 12:26.971
Mr. Hale:
A MOMENT WITH THE ACCUSED?

12:27.010 --> 12:28.773
Sentry: YES, MAGISTRATE.

12:28.810 --> 12:31.199
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

12:31.250 --> 12:33.445
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

12:36.120 --> 12:37.985
Mr. Hale: [ SIGHS ]

12:38.020 --> 12:40.818
Mab: YOU'VE COME HERE
TO KILL ME.

12:40.860 --> 12:44.227
Mr. Hale: IT WOULD BE
WITHIN MY RIGHT TO DO SO.

12:44.260 --> 12:46.387
THE CODE OF THE HIVE IS CLEAR.

12:46.430 --> 12:49.251
BUT, NO, WE HAVE AGREED
TO SPARE YOU.

12:49.300 --> 12:51.222
I WOULD ALLOW NOTHING ELSE.

12:51.270 --> 12:56.060
STILL...TO THE ISSUE AT HAND.

12:56.100 --> 12:58.159
HE WILL INTERROGATE YOU.

12:58.210 --> 13:00.075
Mab:
AND I WILL GIVE HIM NOTHING.

13:00.110 --> 13:04.240
I WILL SWALLOW THE BLACKENED
PILL BEFORE I BETRAY THE CAUSE.

13:04.280 --> 13:06.669
Mr. Hale:
THAT WILL BE YOUR INTENT, YES,

13:06.710 --> 13:07.972
UNTIL HE TORTURES YOU

13:08.020 --> 13:10.648
AND THEN,
HEARING YOUR CRIES OF PAIN,

13:10.690 --> 13:12.180
TORTURES YOU SOME MORE,

13:12.220 --> 13:14.450
AT WHICH POINT
YOU WILL BEG FOR HIM

13:14.490 --> 13:16.082
TO ALLOW YOU TO OFFER A NAME,

13:16.120 --> 13:18.987
EVEN IF ONLY TO RELEASE
YOURSELF FROM THE AGONY.

13:19.030 --> 13:21.089
WHEN THAT HAPPENS --

13:21.130 --> 13:23.860
AND IT WILL HAPPEN...

13:43.350 --> 13:45.614
Anne: WHERE DO YOU GO
AT NIGHT, FATHER?

13:45.650 --> 13:48.881
Mr. Hale: ANNE.
AWAKE AT THIS HOUR?

13:48.920 --> 13:51.559
Anne: MOTHER SAYS
I SHOULDN'T ASK SUCH QUESTIONS,

13:51.590 --> 13:53.455
THAT I SHOULD SIMPLY BE GRATEFUL

13:53.500 --> 13:56.219
FOR THE SACRIFICES YOU MAKE
ON OUR BEHALF.

13:56.260 --> 13:59.161
Mr. Hale: NONSENSE.
ASK WHATEVER YOU LIKE.

13:59.200 --> 14:04.263
TONIGHT I WAS PREOCCUPIED
WITH BUSINESS OF THE TOWN.

14:11.110 --> 14:13.715
Anne: AND DO YOU BELIEVE
SHE IS A WITCH?

14:13.750 --> 14:15.547
Mr. Hale: WHO?

14:15.580 --> 14:17.980
Anne: THE WOMAN YOU SOUGHT OUT
AT THE JAIL.

14:18.020 --> 14:19.715
Mr. Hale: YOU FOLLOWED ME?

14:19.750 --> 14:22.412
Anne: I SIMPLY WANTED TO KNOW
WHAT THOSE SACRIFICES WERE

14:22.460 --> 14:25.088
AND WHY THEY SEEM TO BE
SO OFI'EN MADE IN SECRET.

14:25.130 --> 14:28.258
Mr. Hale: FIRST YOU SNOOP
ABOUT IN MY ROOM,

14:28.300 --> 14:32.760
UNEARTHING MY BELONGINGS,
AND NOW...

14:32.800 --> 14:34.028
[ SIGHS ]

14:34.070 --> 14:36.129
NO.

14:38.440 --> 14:41.000
Anne: NO? WHAT?

14:41.040 --> 14:44.407
Mr. Hale: NO, I DO NOT BELIEVE
SHE IS A WITCH.

14:44.450 --> 14:46.668
SHE IS BUT A SAD, LONELY WOMAN.

14:46.710 --> 14:48.041
Anne: I AM GLAD TO HEAR

14:48.080 --> 14:50.514
THERE IS SOME COMMON SENSE
LEFI' IN SALEM.

14:50.550 --> 14:52.541
GOOD NIGHT, FATHER.

14:52.590 --> 14:53.784
Mr. Hale: GOOD NIGHT, DEAR.

14:58.160 --> 15:00.628
Mab: [ MUFFLED SCREAMING ]

15:00.660 --> 15:02.719
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

15:12.010 --> 15:14.638
[ SCREAMING, GASPING ]

15:14.680 --> 15:17.148
PLEASE! I AM INNOCENT!

15:17.180 --> 15:20.445
Increase: YOU HAVE PLED GUILTY
TO THE PRACTICE OF WITCHCRAI-‘I'.

15:20.480 --> 15:25.144
BUT SUCH A PLEA IS NOT
SUFFICIENT TO SPARE YOUR LIFE.

15:25.190 --> 15:28.819
I WANT NAMES OF OTHERS.

15:28.860 --> 15:31.556
Mab: I KNOW OF NO OTHERS.

15:31.590 --> 15:33.399
Increase: AGAIN.

15:33.430 --> 15:36.228
Mab: NO!
I SWEAR I'M INNOCENT!

15:36.260 --> 15:37.761
[ MUFFLED SCREAMING ]

15:40.840 --> 15:42.330
John: HE'S INSANE.

15:42.370 --> 15:44.838
Cotton: ON A GOOD DAY.

15:56.280 --> 15:58.145
Mab: AAH!

15:58.190 --> 16:01.011
[ GASPING ]

16:01.060 --> 16:03.255
Increase: ONLY THE NAME
OF A FELLOW WITCH

16:03.290 --> 16:04.427
WILL SPARE YOUR LIFE.

16:04.460 --> 16:07.793
Mab: I KNOW OF NO OTHERS.

16:09.130 --> 16:11.963
Increase: I WILL ASK AGAIN,
BUT FIRST A CAUTION.

16:12.000 --> 16:14.935
THE NEXT TIME, THE SALTWATER
THAT FILLED YOUR MOUTH ONLY

16:14.970 --> 16:17.438
WILL TRAVEL DOWN YOUR THROAT
INTO YOUR LUNGS.

16:17.470 --> 16:20.769
AND THEN THE TASTE
YOU STRUGGLE TO DISCERN

16:20.810 --> 16:24.849
WILL NOT BE OF WATER,
NOR OF AIR, BUT OF DEATH.

16:26.980 --> 16:28.345
A NAME.

16:31.750 --> 16:33.411
[ WOOD CREAKING ]
Mab: WAIT!

16:34.920 --> 16:38.856
Increase: AND I WAIT ONLY
FOR THE NAME OF A FELLOW WITCH.

16:41.830 --> 16:44.697
Mab: AND I WILL GIVE IT TO YOU.

16:46.930 --> 16:49.899
HER! GLORIANA!

16:49.940 --> 16:53.376
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

16:55.010 --> 16:56.329
Cotton: NO.

16:56.380 --> 16:59.577
NO. NO. NO!

16:59.610 --> 17:01.646
THIS IS A MISTAKE.
NO, FATHER, THIS IS A MISTAKE.

17:01.680 --> 17:03.318
MISS EMBRY IS NO WITCH.

17:03.350 --> 17:05.238
Increase: YOU ARE HERE
TO OBSERVE, NOT TO INTERFERE.

17:05.290 --> 17:06.518
Cotton: LISTEN TO ME, FATHER.

17:06.550 --> 17:08.415
THIS IS WHAT I HAVE TRIED
TO TELL YOU,

17:08.460 --> 17:11.020
AND NOW I SEE IT TO BE TRUE --
THAT WE HAVE BEEN WRONG.

17:11.060 --> 17:12.925
-Increase: COTTON.
-Cotton: THAT IN OUR ZEAL

17:12.960 --> 17:14.222
TO RID SATAN FROM OUR MIDST,

17:14.260 --> 17:16.353
WE ARE INSTEAD
KILLING INNOCENTS.

17:16.400 --> 17:18.561
Increase: DO NOT PRESUME
TO INSTRUCT ME.

17:18.600 --> 17:21.569
Cotton: WE ARE DOING
THE DEVIL'S WORK FOR HIM!

17:21.600 --> 17:24.330
Increase: AND MY LIFE'S WORK
IS A MISTAKE?

17:24.370 --> 17:28.602
Cotton: RESPECT FU LLY. . .YES.

17:28.640 --> 17:31.609
Increase: STAND ASIDE.

17:31.650 --> 17:33.743
Cotton: PLEASE, FATHER,
I BEG YOU -- SPARE HER.

17:33.780 --> 17:35.042
Increase: GET OUT OF MY WAY.

17:35.080 --> 17:36.069
Cotton: LISTEN TO ME!

17:37.920 --> 17:39.342
Increase: I HAVE.

17:39.390 --> 17:42.689
AND I WILL NO LONGER LET YOU
ACT THE FOOL.

17:42.720 --> 17:45.484
Cotton: YOU ARE SURE IT IS I
WHO ACTS THE FOOL?

17:47.300 --> 17:48.995
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]
Gloriana: COTTON.

17:52.100 --> 17:54.933
Increase: TAKE HER TO THE CAGE.

17:56.770 --> 17:59.534
Gloriana: COTTON. COTTON!

17:59.570 --> 18:01.606
Cotton: NO.
[ PANTING ]

18:01.640 --> 18:06.009
Gloriana: COTTON! COTTON!

18:17.460 --> 18:21.590
George: [ GAGGING ]

18:21.630 --> 18:24.428
Isaac: OH, LORD.
WHAT IS IT, MR. SIBLEY?

18:24.470 --> 18:26.062
George: [ GROANING ]

18:26.100 --> 18:29.069
Isaac: TRY TO BREATHE,
MR. SIBLEY. THAT'S IT.

18:29.100 --> 18:30.408
George: [ GROANING ]

18:30.440 --> 18:32.931
Isaac:
SLOW BREATH, MR. SIBLEY.

18:32.970 --> 18:34.733
THAT'S RIGHT.
[ EXHALES HEAVILY ]

18:34.780 --> 18:37.101
THAT'S IT, NICE AND EASY.

18:38.480 --> 18:39.401
NO!

18:46.890 --> 18:48.858
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

18:57.300 --> 18:59.393
George: [ GROANING ]

19:34.000 --> 19:35.558
[ FROG SQUEAKING ]

19:47.280 --> 19:48.349
[ BELL CHIMING ]

19:48.380 --> 19:50.985
Cotton: FATHER!

19:51.020 --> 19:52.749
FATHER, YOU HAVE NO EVIDENCE.

19:52.790 --> 19:56.248
Increase: NONSENSE. I HAVE
THE WORD OF AN ADMITTED WITCH.

19:56.290 --> 19:59.054
Cotton: A WOMAN WHO PRACTICES
THE DEVIL'S CRAFI'?

19:59.090 --> 20:00.728
YOU TRUST HER TO FINGER OTHERS?

20:00.760 --> 20:02.352
Increase: TELL ME --

20:02.400 --> 20:05.324
DO ALL ACCUSATIONS STIR
SUCH PASSIONS IN YOU?

20:05.370 --> 20:08.589
OR IS THERE SOMETHING UNIQUE
ABOUT THE WHORE'S CASE?

20:08.640 --> 20:12.758
Cotton: I KNOW THESE PEOPLE.
I HAVE LIVED AMONG THEM.

20:12.810 --> 20:16.200
MISS EMBRY IS NO TOOL OF SATAN.

20:16.240 --> 20:21.018
Increase: AND IF SHE WERE TO BE
EXAMINED FOR THE DEVIL'S MARKS?

20:21.050 --> 20:25.089
Cotton: AN EXAMINATION?

20:25.120 --> 20:26.883
I'M CONFIDENT --

20:26.920 --> 20:29.912
NO, I AM CERTAIN --
THAT YOU WOULD FIND NOTHING.

20:29.960 --> 20:33.259
IN FACT, YES, I WOULD ENCOURAGE
YOU TO SE'I'I'LE THE ISSUE

20:33.300 --> 20:34.790
AND CONDUCT THE EXAM AT ONCE.

20:34.830 --> 20:38.527
Increase: ME? NO.

20:38.570 --> 20:41.437
NO, I WILL LEAVE THAT TO YOU.

20:41.470 --> 20:45.065
[ ROOSTER CROWS ]

20:45.110 --> 20:48.136
YOU WILL EXAMINE THE ACCUSED.

20:50.680 --> 20:54.138
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

21:00.190 --> 21:01.919
Mary: CAPTAIN.

21:03.630 --> 21:05.222
NO.

21:05.260 --> 21:06.625
JOHN!

21:12.030 --> 21:14.066
John: THAT WASN'T THE REACTION
I WAS EXPECTING.

21:14.100 --> 21:16.660
Mary: NOR THE GREETING I WAS.

21:19.270 --> 21:22.068
WHAT WE SAID...WHAT WE DID.

21:22.110 --> 21:23.941
John: WHAT, DO YOU REGRET IT?

21:23.980 --> 21:26.301
Mary: NO.

21:26.350 --> 21:29.717
MY ONLY REGRET IS THAT IT
CAN NEVER HAPPEN AGAIN.

21:31.220 --> 21:34.018
I'M A MARRIED WOMAN, JOHN.

21:34.060 --> 21:36.255
John: WITH A VERY SICK HUSBAND.

21:36.290 --> 21:39.657
Mary: MR. SIBLEY WOULD NEVER DO
ME THE FAVOR OF DYING.

21:39.690 --> 21:40.850
WE BOTH KNOW THAT.

21:40.900 --> 21:42.788
John:
HE WAS TAKEN TO HOSPITAL.

21:42.830 --> 21:45.025
Mary: FROM WHERE HE
WILL SURELY RETURN...

21:45.070 --> 21:47.937
AS ALIVE AND MARRIED AS EVER.

21:47.970 --> 21:50.962
John: IS THAT THE REASON?

21:51.010 --> 21:52.705
SIBLEY?

21:52.740 --> 21:54.139
NOTHING ELSE?

21:54.180 --> 21:55.772
NOT A FEAR?

21:55.810 --> 21:59.701
OR A SECRET THAT YOU THINK
I COULDN'T ACCEPT?

21:59.750 --> 22:01.945
BECAUSE THERE IS
NO ONE IN SALEM

22:01.980 --> 22:03.686
UNBURDENED BY THEIR PAST...

22:03.720 --> 22:06.814
NOT EVEN ME.

22:08.020 --> 22:10.159
Mary: I'M SORRY, JOHN.

22:14.700 --> 22:17.157
I HOPE YOU CAN UNDERSTAND.

22:32.950 --> 22:35.510
Cotton: FATHER, PLEASE.

22:35.550 --> 22:37.177
Increase: PROCEED.

22:46.890 --> 22:48.448
Gloriana: [ GASPS ]

22:54.070 --> 22:55.697
Cotton: NO MARKS.

22:55.740 --> 22:57.367
Increase: TURN HER.

23:10.550 --> 23:11.778
Cotton: NOTHING.

23:11.820 --> 23:13.754
Increase: RAISE HER SMOCK.

23:25.670 --> 23:27.638
STILL NOTHING.

23:27.670 --> 23:29.968
Increase: THE UPPER TORSO.

23:34.440 --> 23:36.374
Gloriana: [ GASPS ]

23:36.410 --> 23:38.605
Cotton: [ SIGHS ]

23:38.650 --> 23:40.299
FATHER...

23:40.350 --> 23:42.341
Increase: THE UPPER TORSO.

24:15.520 --> 24:17.340
WAIT.

24:23.960 --> 24:25.188
Gloriana: [ SNIFFS ]

24:35.370 --> 24:37.509
Cotton: SO, YOU SEE,
AS I ASSURED YOU,

24:37.540 --> 24:39.303
SHE BEARS NO SIGNS
OF A DEVIL'S AGENT,

24:39.340 --> 24:41.171
NO BLEMISH ES,
NO WITCHES' TEATS.

24:41.210 --> 24:43.770
Increase: ALL OF WHICH I WILL BE
SURE TO MENTION AT HER TRIAL.

24:43.810 --> 24:45.346
Cotton: HER TRIAL?

24:45.380 --> 24:48.543
BUT I HAVE PROVEN TO YOU
SHE IS WITHOUT MARKS.

24:48.580 --> 24:52.141
Increase: HAVE YOU FORGOTTEN?
WE ARE NOT JUDGES.

24:52.190 --> 24:54.954
WE ARE SIMPLY SEEKERS
OF THE TRUTH.

24:54.990 --> 24:58.323
THE POWER OF VERDICT RESTS
WITH THE SELECTMEN.

24:58.360 --> 25:00.828
Cotton: THIS IS SALEM.
YOU KNOW HOW THEY WILL VOTE.

25:00.860 --> 25:02.828
Increase: WELL, THEN YOU SAVE

25:02.860 --> 25:05.499
YOUR RAGE AND YOUR IMPUDENCE
FOR THEM.

25:15.540 --> 25:17.872
[ SILVERWARE CLINKING ]

25:22.720 --> 25:26.588
Anne: ANOTHER WOMAN WAS ACCUSED
TODAY...AS YOU SAW.

25:26.620 --> 25:29.509
IT'S MADNESS, THIS WITCH PANIC.

25:29.560 --> 25:31.653
Mr. Hale:
YES, IT IS REGRETTABLE.

25:31.690 --> 25:33.749
Anne: REGRET—TABLE?

25:33.800 --> 25:35.153
Mr. Hale:
WHAT WOULD YOU HAVE ME DO?

25:37.570 --> 25:40.869
YOU HAVE ANY NUMBER OF OPTIONS
BEYOND NOTHING.

25:40.900 --> 25:43.437
Mr. Hale: IAM ONE MAN. PERHAPS
YOU EXPECT TOO MUCH OF ME.

25:43.470 --> 25:45.006
Anne: PERHAPS YOU ARE CONTENT
WITH TOO LITTLE.

25:45.040 --> 25:48.009
Mrs. Hale:
HOLD YOUR TONGUE, CHILD.

25:48.040 --> 25:50.099
Anne: [SIGHS]
I JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND

25:50.140 --> 25:53.405
WHY HE'S SO CONTENT
TO SEE PEOPLE HANG...

25:53.450 --> 25:55.338
ALMOST AS IF HE
SECRETLY LIKES IT.

25:55.380 --> 25:58.019
Mr. Hale: I DON'T APPRECIATE
THE INSINUATION.

25:58.050 --> 26:00.610
Anne: WHAT INSINUATION IS THAT?

26:00.660 --> 26:02.082
Mr. Hale: THAT I WAS
SOMEHOW IN LEAGUE

26:02.120 --> 26:03.678
WITH THE MURDERING PURITANS.

26:03.730 --> 26:05.948
Anne: OH, NO, THAT WAS NOT
MY INSINUATION AT ALL.

26:07.490 --> 26:09.549
IN FACT,
IT WAS QUITE THE OPPOSITE.

26:11.300 --> 26:13.359
Mr. Hale:
AND WHAT MIGHT THAT BE?

26:13.400 --> 26:17.291
Anne: YOU KNOW, I'M --
I'M SUDDENLY VERY TIRED.

26:17.340 --> 26:18.637
Mr. Hale:
WHAT ARE YOU ACCUSING ME OF?

26:18.670 --> 26:20.706
Anne:
I THINK I SHOULD LIE DOWN.

26:20.740 --> 26:23.072
Mr. Hale:
ANNE, DO NOT WALK AWAY UNTIL
YOU HAVE EXPLAINED YOURSELF.

26:23.110 --> 26:24.748
ANNE!

26:31.690 --> 26:33.681
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

26:37.490 --> 26:39.924
John: MAY I ASK YOU A QUESTION?

26:39.960 --> 26:42.155
WHY DOES HE HATE YOU?

26:42.200 --> 26:43.997
Cotton: TWO REASONS ONLY --

26:44.030 --> 26:46.169
FOR WHAT I AM...

26:46.200 --> 26:49.897
AND WHAT I AM NOT.

26:49.940 --> 26:51.999
John: AND YOU'VE APPEALED TO HIM
ON THE GIRL'S BEHALF?

26:52.040 --> 26:55.578
Cotton: REPEATEDLY.
HE DOES NOT REGARD ME.

26:55.610 --> 27:00.172
TRUTH TOLD, HE DOES NOT REGARD
ANYONE EXCEPT...

27:00.210 --> 27:02.314
FOR YOU, JOHN.

27:02.350 --> 27:03.840
John: COTTON, NO.

27:03.890 --> 27:07.189
Cotton: YOU ARE EVERYTHING
HE EVER WISHED ME TO BE.

27:07.220 --> 27:09.586
YOU ARE A HERO IN WAR.

27:09.620 --> 27:14.023
YOU ARE A MAN WITHOUT WEAKNESS
OR FRAILTY.

27:14.060 --> 27:17.097
John: COTTON, I'M SORRY.

27:17.130 --> 27:21.635
BEGGING ANOTHER PURITAN ASSHOLE
TO DO THE RIGHT THING?

27:21.670 --> 27:24.798
SINCE WHEN HAS IT WORKED?

27:24.840 --> 27:28.173
-AND WHY WOULD IT WORK NOW?
-Cotton: YOU'RE RIGHT.

27:28.210 --> 27:32.146
NO MAN SHOULD BE FORCED TO
HUMBLE HIMSELF BEFORE MY FATHER.

27:32.180 --> 27:36.378
I HAVE BEEN IN SALEM
FOR MONTHS.

27:36.420 --> 27:40.049
I HAVE MADE ALLIES AND ENEMIES
IN SCORES.

27:40.090 --> 27:43.184
BUT THE CLOSEST THING THAT
I HAVE COME TO A FRIEND...

27:45.890 --> 27:47.892
...IS YOU.

27:47.930 --> 27:50.558
SO I ASK YOU --

27:50.600 --> 27:54.297
I BEG YOU --

27:54.340 --> 27:56.729
TO APPEAL TO MY FATHER,

27:56.770 --> 28:00.035
IF THERE IS
SOME SMALL PART OF YOU

28:00.070 --> 28:02.334
THAT CAN CALL ME
A FRIEND, TOO.

28:06.180 --> 28:08.011
Isaac: [ BREATHING HEAVILY]

28:08.050 --> 28:10.177
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

28:16.460 --> 28:18.018
MR. SIBLEY?

28:43.620 --> 28:46.088
MR. SIBLEY?!

28:53.660 --> 28:55.958
MR. SIBLEY?!

29:07.010 --> 29:10.036
MR. SIBLEY.

29:10.080 --> 29:12.275
George: HELP ME, ISAAC.

29:12.310 --> 29:13.345
[ GROANS ]

29:15.280 --> 29:17.748
Isaac: YOU CAN SPEAK.

29:17.790 --> 29:20.645
George:
THE LORD'S MIRACULOUS WORKINGS.

29:20.690 --> 29:22.908
Isaac: YOU'RE LEAKING BLOOD.

29:22.960 --> 29:26.157
George: WHICH IS WHYI NEED
YOUR HELP. [ GROANING ]

29:26.190 --> 29:28.920
GO TO SALEM.

29:28.960 --> 29:34.068
RETURN WITH SUPPLIES
AND ONE TO ADMINISTER THEM.

29:34.100 --> 29:36.466
Isaac: HELP YOU?

29:36.500 --> 29:39.503
George: YES.

29:41.510 --> 29:43.978
Isaac: DO YOU REMEMBER THE DAY
YOU MARKED ME?

29:46.280 --> 29:51.149
THE DAY YOU SEARED MY FLESH
WITH THE SIGN OF THE FORNICATOR?

29:51.190 --> 29:53.681
YOU REMEMBER THAT?

29:53.720 --> 29:58.350
George: AND I WOULD IMAGINE THAT
NOT A MOMENT HAS SINCE PASSED

29:58.390 --> 30:00.028
THAT YOU DIDN'T WISH ME DEAD.

30:00.060 --> 30:06.420
AND NOW YOUR CHANCE,
WITHOUT EVEN RAISING A HAND.

30:06.470 --> 30:10.338
WALK AWAY,
AND I WILL SURELY DIE HERE.

30:10.370 --> 30:12.930
[ GROANING ]

30:12.970 --> 30:14.938
Isaac: WHY SHOULDN'T I?

30:14.980 --> 30:19.098
George: BECAUSE WHILE
YOU DESIRED REVENGE

30:19.150 --> 30:23.769
[GROANS]
I BORE REGRET FOR WHAT I DID.

30:23.820 --> 30:27.278
Isaac: WORDS.

30:27.320 --> 30:29.959
George: THEN HELP ME,
AND I WILL SHOWER YOU

30:29.990 --> 30:33.050
NOT WITH WORDS, BUT GOLD,

30:33.090 --> 30:36.890
MORE THAN YOU'VE EVER HOPED
TO POSSESS.

30:36.930 --> 30:38.693
[ GROANS ]

30:38.730 --> 30:40.129
Isaac: GOLD?

30:40.170 --> 30:43.389
TO RETURN WITH -- WITH MEDICINES
AND MRS. SIBLEY?

30:43.440 --> 30:44.566
George: NO.
[ GROANS ]

30:44.610 --> 30:45.634
NOT HER.

30:45.670 --> 30:47.877
INCREASE.

30:47.910 --> 30:49.400
Isaac: INCREASE?

30:49.440 --> 30:51.305
George: TELL MY WIFE NOTHING.

30:51.350 --> 30:55.013
BRING ME INCREASE MATHER
AT ONCE.

30:57.450 --> 30:59.589
GO NOW, BOY!

30:59.620 --> 31:02.214
RUN!

31:02.260 --> 31:03.921
RUN!

31:03.960 --> 31:05.848
RUN!

31:05.890 --> 31:07.755
[ GROANING ]

31:16.700 --> 31:18.907
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

31:31.990 --> 31:33.787
[ PEN SCRATCHING ]

31:35.990 --> 31:37.753
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

31:37.790 --> 31:39.724
Increase: YES?

31:43.060 --> 31:44.527
John: REVEREND.

31:44.570 --> 31:47.130
Increase: THE ANSWER IS NO.

31:47.170 --> 31:49.138
John: I DIDN'T ASK A QUESTION.

31:49.170 --> 31:52.037
Increase: YOU'RE HERE TO BEG FOR
THE WHORE'S LIFE, ARE YOU NOT?

31:52.070 --> 31:55.130
DISPATCHED BY MY BESOTTED SON,
NO DOUBT.

31:55.180 --> 31:57.034
John: YES.

31:57.080 --> 32:01.039
Increase: WELL, LET ME SAVE YOU
THE TROUBLE, CAPTAIN ALDEN.

32:01.080 --> 32:04.379
THE DECISION HAS BEEN MADE
TO TAKE HER TO TRIAL.

32:04.420 --> 32:08.982
BUT REST ASSURED
I WILL BE SURE TO TELL COTTON

32:09.020 --> 32:11.386
THAT YOUR PLEAS
WERE MOST HEARTFELT.

32:11.430 --> 32:14.820
John:
SIR...GLORIANA IS NO WITCH.

32:14.860 --> 32:16.498
Increase: NO.

32:16.530 --> 32:20.466
BUT I THINK YOU WILL AGREE
SHE HAS BEWITCHED MY SON.

32:24.310 --> 32:26.904
John: YOU KNOW, MY FATHER HELD
YOU IN HIGH REGARD, REVEREND.

32:26.940 --> 32:29.431
Increase:
ALDEN SR. WAS A GOOD MAN.

32:29.480 --> 32:32.301
HE VIEWED THE WORLD
WITH UNCOMMON REASON.

32:32.350 --> 32:35.911
John: YEAH, WELL, EXCEPT
WHEN IT CAME TO HIS OWN SON.

32:35.950 --> 32:38.748
Increase: [ SIGHS ]

32:38.790 --> 32:41.782
John: HE WANTED ME
TO STUDY SCRIPTURE,

32:41.820 --> 32:44.584
AND I CHOSE
TO EXPLORE THE WOODS.

32:44.630 --> 32:46.951
HE WANTED ME
TO ATTEND UNIVERSITY,

32:46.990 --> 32:48.799
AND I VOLUNTEERED FOR WAR.

32:48.830 --> 32:52.698
HE WENT TO HIS GRAVE THINKING
MY LIFE'S CHOICES MISTAKES.

32:57.200 --> 33:00.601
Increase: AND YET HE ALLOWED YOU
TO MAKE THEM.

33:00.640 --> 33:02.870
John: WELL, THAT'S BECAUSE
HE KNEW THE DIFFERENCE.

33:02.910 --> 33:04.309
Increase: BETWEEN?

33:04.350 --> 33:06.648
John: BETWEEN LOVING
HIS SON'S CHOICES

33:06.680 --> 33:08.819
AND LOVING HIS SON.

33:08.850 --> 33:11.045
Increase: [ SIGHS ]

33:15.590 --> 33:17.558
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

33:17.590 --> 33:19.023
[ FOOTSTEPS DEPARTING ]

33:20.690 --> 33:22.226
[ DOG BARKING ]

33:22.260 --> 33:23.295
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

33:23.330 --> 33:25.059
Isaac: [ PANTING ]

33:25.100 --> 33:26.465
CAPTAIN ALDEN.

33:26.500 --> 33:28.536
John: ISAAC, WHAT IS IT?

33:28.570 --> 33:31.266
Isaac: NOT HERE.

33:34.040 --> 33:36.008
John: GEORGE SIBLEY CAN SPEAK?

33:37.740 --> 33:39.469
John: AND WOUNDED,
HE DOESN'T REQUEST HIS WIFE,

33:39.510 --> 33:41.148
-BUT ASKS FOR --
-Isaac: INCREASE MATHER.

33:41.180 --> 33:42.477
[ PANTING ]

33:42.520 --> 33:45.546
I TRUST HIM
NO MORE THAN A THIEF.

33:45.590 --> 33:48.855
BUT TO DISOBEY A MAN
OF HIS STANDING?

33:48.890 --> 33:50.915
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:50.960 --> 33:52.552
John: THEN DO NOTHING.

33:54.860 --> 33:56.555
Isaac: CAPTAIN?

33:56.600 --> 34:00.661
John: YOU SOUGHT MY ADVICE,
SO I OFFER IT.

34:00.700 --> 34:02.668
DO NOTHING.

34:02.700 --> 34:04.509
Isaac:
BUT TO LEAVE HIM ANY LONGER

34:04.540 --> 34:06.428
THAN I HAVE IN THE WOODS,
BLEEDING...

34:06.470 --> 34:08.176
John: HE WILL DIE.

34:08.210 --> 34:12.203
Isaac: YES.

34:12.250 --> 34:15.048
John: DOES HE DESERVE
ANYTHING LESS?

34:15.080 --> 34:17.742
THE MAN WHO MARKED
YOUR FLESH...

34:17.780 --> 34:19.839
DROVE ME TO WAR...

34:19.890 --> 34:23.519
AND HAS RULED OVER SALEM
LIKE A POWER-MAD KING?

34:23.560 --> 34:26.028
AND NOW, WHAT,
HE BEGS FOR COMPASSION?

34:26.060 --> 34:28.551
[ SCOFFS ]
COOPERATION?

34:32.330 --> 34:34.469
WHAT?

34:34.500 --> 34:37.560
Isaac: [ SIGHS ]

34:37.600 --> 34:40.467
I KNOW YOU LOVE HER, CAPTAIN.

34:40.510 --> 34:44.105
BUT TO LEAVE HIM TO DIE
IS MURDER.

34:46.780 --> 34:51.285
John: DO...NOTHING.

35:01.330 --> 35:04.766
Gloriana: NO.
WHERE ARE YOU TAKING ME?

35:06.430 --> 35:09.558
TELL ME!
WHERE ARE YOU TAKING ME?!

35:09.600 --> 35:12.728
Increase: GOOD PEOPLE OF SALEM,

35:12.770 --> 35:15.830
IT HAS COME TO MY ATTENTION

35:15.880 --> 35:19.577
THAT THE ACCUSATION
LEVELED TODAY

35:19.610 --> 35:22.738
WAS A TRICK OF THE WITCHES...

35:22.780 --> 35:28.412
AN INFERNAL PLOY TO DELUDE AND
DISTRACT FROM THE TRULY GUILTY.

35:28.460 --> 35:33.921
THIS WOMAN IS NO SORCERESS.

35:33.960 --> 35:38.192
AND THEREFORE SHE WILL NOT GO
TO TRIAL.

35:38.230 --> 35:40.323
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

35:43.070 --> 35:47.700
BUT WHAT HER ADVOCATES FAIL
TO GRASP

35:47.740 --> 35:52.848
IS THAT ABSENCE OF GUILT
DOES NOT MEAN INNOCENCE...

35:52.880 --> 35:58.386
FOR THIS WHORE IS NO INNOCENT --
FAR FROM IT.

35:58.420 --> 36:01.787
SHE IS GUILTY OF SIN,
SINS OF THE FLESH,

36:01.820 --> 36:05.221
SINS AGAINST GOD,
SINS BOTH MORTAL AND ETERNAL,

36:05.260 --> 36:09.458
AND AS SUCH, SHE WARRANTS
NO PLACE IN SALEM.

36:09.500 --> 36:10.558
Cotton: NO.

36:10.600 --> 36:12.989
Increase: AND SO, BY MY DECREE,

36:13.030 --> 36:15.965
SHE IS HEREBY BANISHED
FROM OUR MIDST,

36:16.000 --> 36:20.334
HER EXPULSION IMMEDIATE
AND BEYOND DISPUTE.

36:20.370 --> 36:23.578
Increase: AND SHOULD SHE --
LOOK AT ME --

36:23.610 --> 36:28.809
EVER RETURN AT ANY TIME,

36:28.850 --> 36:30.647
FOR ANY REASON,

36:30.680 --> 36:33.979
YOU WILL FIND YOURSELF ONCE
AGAIN BESIDE ME ON THE COMMON,

36:34.020 --> 36:36.159
YOUR LIFELESS BODY DANGLING

36:36.190 --> 36:39.159
FROM THE WRONG END
OF THE HANGMAN'S NOOSE.

36:39.190 --> 36:41.351
-TAKE HER.
-G|oriana: COTTON!

36:41.400 --> 36:43.891
-Cotton: GLORIANA!
-G|oriana: COTTON! COTTON!

36:43.930 --> 36:46.091
COTTON! COTTON!

36:46.130 --> 36:48.394
-Cotton: GLORIANA!
-Man: STAND BACK. STAY BACK.

36:48.440 --> 36:50.795
-G|oriana: [CRYING]
-Cotton: NO! GLORIANA!

36:56.740 --> 36:57.832
[ HOOVES CLOPPING ]

36:57.880 --> 36:59.848
I'M SORRY.

36:59.880 --> 37:01.438
Gloriana: [ CRYING ]

37:04.080 --> 37:07.481
Increase: TAKE HER AS FAR
AS YOUR STEEDS WILL TRAVEL.

37:10.320 --> 37:13.027
AND LET IT BE KNOWN

37:13.060 --> 37:16.120
NEITHER SIN NOR SINNER

37:16.160 --> 37:19.960
HAVE ANY PLACE IN SALEM.

37:29.240 --> 37:30.673
[ FROG SQUEAKING ]

37:39.120 --> 37:41.384
Mary: GEORGE.

37:41.420 --> 37:44.116
I DON'T KNOW HOW OR BY WHOM,

37:44.160 --> 37:46.924
BUT THE FAMILIAR
HAS BEEN EXCISED FROM HIM.

37:46.960 --> 37:50.589
HE COULD BE ANYWHERE RIGHT NOW,
TALKING TO ANYONE.

37:50.630 --> 37:52.291
ALL THAT WE'VE WORKED FOR,

37:52.330 --> 37:55.458
ALL THAT I'VE SACRIFICED,
INCINERATED IN AN INSTANT.

37:55.500 --> 37:57.798
Tituba: CALM YOURSELF
AND HELP ME.

38:15.490 --> 38:19.358
Mary:
MUTARE, ET NOTUM SUMBOTIS.

38:19.390 --> 38:22.359
Tituba:
FORMA ENIM ESSE OSTENDIT.

38:22.400 --> 38:24.994
CORPUS, ANIMA, MENS.

38:25.030 --> 38:27.464
LEAD ME TO THE ONE I SEEK.

38:34.910 --> 38:37.777
[ OWL SCREECHES ]

38:37.810 --> 38:40.199
THE CREATURE
WILL LEAD ME TO HIM.

38:40.250 --> 38:43.617
WITH LUCK,
I WILL FIND HIM QUICKLY.

38:43.650 --> 38:46.414
Mary: AND WITHOUT IT,
WE SHALL ALL BURN.

39:01.440 --> 39:05.536
Increase: YOU TAKE ISSUE
WITH MY METHODS.

39:05.570 --> 39:09.176
I UNDERSTAND.

39:09.210 --> 39:13.806
WHAT YOU NEED TO UNDERSTAND IS
THAT EVERYTHING I HAVE DONE

39:13.850 --> 39:17.741
HAS BEEN TO MAKE YOU WORTHY
OF THE MATHER NAME.

39:19.750 --> 39:21.809
Cotton: I LOVED HER.

39:21.860 --> 39:23.987
Increase: DO NOT SAY THAT.

39:24.020 --> 39:28.423
Cotton: MY SILENCE
DOES NOT MAKE IT UNTRUE.

39:28.460 --> 39:31.258
Increase: ONE DAY,

39:31.300 --> 39:37.535
WHEN YOU ARE GOVERNOR
OF THIS GREAT LAND,

39:37.570 --> 39:43.270
A MAN OF POWER
AND A MODEL OF VIRTUE,

39:43.310 --> 39:46.939
RESPECT ED AND FEARED
IN EQUAL MEASURE,

39:46.980 --> 39:49.710
YOU WILL TRACE IT BACK
TO THIS DAY...

39:49.750 --> 39:52.241
Cotton: [ SIGHS ]

39:52.290 --> 39:56.249
Increase: ...THE DAYI REMOVED
TEMPTATION FROM YOUR PATH.

40:09.770 --> 40:10.930
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

40:20.510 --> 40:22.478
-YOU THERE.
-Woman: YES?

40:22.520 --> 40:25.648
Increase: BRING ME SOME BLACK
TEA, VERY STRONG, IF YOU PLEASE.

40:25.690 --> 40:27.089
Woman: MM-HMM.

40:32.090 --> 40:33.978
Increase:
ARE YOU NOT THE YOUNG MAN

40:34.030 --> 40:37.488
WHO TRANSPORTED MR. SIBLEY
TO BOSTON YESTERDAY?

40:37.530 --> 40:40.658
Isaac: ISAAC, SIR.

40:40.700 --> 40:42.463
-Increase: ISAAC.
-Isaac: MM.

40:42.500 --> 40:44.809
Increase: BOSTON AND BACK?
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:44.840 --> 40:46.637
RECORD TIME.

40:46.670 --> 40:48.501
YOU MUST BE
QUITE THE HORSEMAN, ISAAC.

40:48.540 --> 40:51.179
Isaac:
NO, I-I WOULDN'T SAY THAT.

40:51.210 --> 40:53.075
Increase: WELL, TELL ME.

40:53.110 --> 40:56.614
DID THE PHYSICIAN OFFER
ANY INSIGHT

40:56.650 --> 40:59.346
INTO THE PATIENT'S CONDITION?

40:59.390 --> 41:02.780
Isaac: PHYSICIAN?

41:02.820 --> 41:06.620
Increase: A DIAGNOSIS?
OR A PROGNOSIS?

41:06.660 --> 41:09.697
Isaac: UM...

41:09.730 --> 41:12.369
NO, I CAN'T...

41:13.530 --> 41:15.464
Increase:
WELL, YOU DID TAKE MR. SIBLEY

41:15.500 --> 41:17.468
TO THE HOSPITAL, DID YOU NOT?

41:17.500 --> 41:21.778
WHAT IS IT
YOU ARE NOT SAYING?

41:21.810 --> 41:25.143
ISAAC...LOOK AT ME.

41:28.980 --> 41:31.540
TELL ME THE TRUTH
ABOUT YOUR JOURNEY.

41:38.560 --> 41:41.449
THE INJURED
IS DUE SOUTH, INLAND,

41:41.490 --> 41:43.890
ON THE WOODED PATH TO BOSTON.

41:46.400 --> 41:47.560
HYAH!

41:47.600 --> 41:49.067
Man: CLEAR THE WAY.

41:49.100 --> 41:50.692
[ OWL SCREECHING ]

42:34.280 --> 42:37.374
Mab: [ GULPS]

42:40.090 --> 42:41.648
[ GROANING ]

43:05.510 --> 43:06.909
[ HORSE NEIGHING ]

43:30.340 --> 43:32.604
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

43:32.640 --> 43:35.336
George: WHO'S THERE?
SHOW YOURSELF.

43:35.380 --> 43:37.678
WHO ARE YOU?

43:37.710 --> 43:39.507
Petrus: THE NAME IS PETRUS.

43:39.550 --> 43:42.849
NOT AN HOUR AGO,
I SPIED YOU SLEEPING,

43:42.880 --> 43:46.680
AND, SEEING YOUR GRAVE WOUND,
I HAVE RETURNED WITH MEDICINALS.

43:46.720 --> 43:49.951
George: STOP.
NOT ONE STEP CLOSER. [ GROANS ]

43:49.990 --> 43:52.925
Petrus: BUT, SIR, AN INFECTION
HAS ALREADY TAKEN ROOT.

43:52.960 --> 43:56.350
George: DO NOT WORRY YOURSELF.
AID IS ON THE WAY.

43:56.400 --> 43:57.799
[ GROANING ]

43:57.830 --> 44:00.264
Petrus: BUT YOU ARE IN PAIN,
ARE YOU NOT?

44:00.300 --> 44:06.102
I HAVE CONCOCT ED A SIMPLE PHYSIC
TO EASE YOUR SUFFERING.

44:06.140 --> 44:11.942
NO CREATURE, MAN OR ANIMAL,
SHOULD SUFFER AS YOU DO, SIR.

44:11.980 --> 44:13.709
George: [ GROANS ]

44:13.750 --> 44:15.342
Petrus: PLEASE.

44:22.360 --> 44:24.578
[GULPS]

44:26.760 --> 44:30.457
[ COUGHING ]

44:30.500 --> 44:32.968
WHAT HAVE YOU GIVEN ME?

44:33.000 --> 44:34.160
[ GAGGING ]

44:34.200 --> 44:36.862
Petrus:
I AM TRULY SORRY, SIR.

44:41.210 --> 44:42.871
SHE MADE ME.

44:46.850 --> 44:48.818
Tituba: WE WILL TAKE HIM
TO YOUR SHACK

44:48.850 --> 44:50.317
UNTIL THE THREAT HAS PASSED.

44:50.350 --> 44:52.910
DID YOU REALLY THINK
IT WOULD BE SO EASY

44:52.950 --> 44:56.283
TO ESCAPE US, MR. SIBLEY?

44:58.460 --> 45:02.521
Increase: THERE, UP AHEAD!

45:07.570 --> 45:10.596
GEORGE? GEORGE?

45:15.240 --> 45:17.003
YOU'RE THE SERVANT?

45:17.040 --> 45:18.849
Tituba: YES, SIR,
SENT BY MRS. SIBLEY

45:18.880 --> 45:20.347
TO RETRIEVE
HER AILING HUSBAND.

45:20.380 --> 45:22.746
Increase: THIS IS WORSE
THAN I HAD FEARED.

45:22.780 --> 45:24.748
Tituba: WHICH IS WHY HE NEEDS
TO BE TAKEN TO HOSPITAL AT ONCE.

45:24.790 --> 45:26.041
Increase: NO.

45:26.090 --> 45:28.854
IT IS NOT THE INJURY
THAT TROUBLES ME,

45:28.890 --> 45:31.108
BUT HOW HE CAME BY IT.

45:31.160 --> 45:33.628
HE SOUGHT TO FREE HIMSELF
FROM THE WITCHES' GRIP.

45:33.660 --> 45:35.389
Tituba: I DO NOT UNDERSTAND.

45:35.430 --> 45:36.829
Increase: THE MAN IS NOT ILL.

45:38.160 --> 45:41.368
HE HAS BEEN SPELLED.

45:41.400 --> 45:43.960
MIGHT YOU KNOW
SOMETHING ABOUT THAT?

45:45.670 --> 45:48.309
[ BELL CHIMING ]

45:48.340 --> 45:50.433
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

45:50.480 --> 45:52.471
John: MISS HALE.

45:52.510 --> 45:54.603
Anne: DO YOU REMEMBER
THAT AFTERNOON IN THE GRAVEYARD,

45:54.650 --> 45:56.470
WHEN YOU IMPLIED MY FATHER
IS NOT WHO HE SEEMS?

45:56.520 --> 45:58.545
John: YES.

45:58.580 --> 46:02.118
Anne: INVITE ME INSIDE,
AND I'LL TELL YOU WHY I AGREE.

46:20.140 --> 46:22.506
Mary:
TELL ME -- WHERE IS MR. SIBLEY?

46:22.540 --> 46:24.007
Tituba: WE HAVE A PROBLEM.

46:24.040 --> 46:25.473
Mary: THAT WAS NOT MY QUESTION.

46:25.510 --> 46:27.307
EITHER YOU KNOW WHERE HE IS,
OR YOU DON'T.

46:27.350 --> 46:28.647
Tituba: I DO KNOW WHERE HE IS,

46:28.680 --> 46:30.318
AND THAT IS THE PROBLEM.

46:30.350 --> 46:32.910
THE REVEREND HAS DEEMED HIM
A VICTIM OF WITCHCRAFT

46:32.950 --> 46:36.249
AND HAS DECIDED THAT GEORGE
IS TO REST UNDER HIS CARE.

46:36.290 --> 46:38.679
Increase:
QUICKLY NOW. MAKE HASTE.

46:38.720 --> 46:40.426
Mary: MY GOD.

46:40.460 --> 46:42.758
Tituba: PETRUS' PHYSIC
WILL LAST BUT A DAY.

46:42.800 --> 46:44.449
Increase: THERE. THERE.

46:44.500 --> 46:47.822
Tituba: AND THEN MR. SIBLEY
WILL AWAKE, LUCID AND EAGER.

46:47.870 --> 46:50.862
Mary:
TO TELL INCREASE EVERYTHING.
